DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_9ebde1cd-ecfd-4ede-942a-fd7823e3e162'[Year],
			"Total_Sales", 'Walmart'[Total_Sales],
			"MinDate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('LocalDateTable_9ebde1cd-ecfd-4ede-942a-fd7823e3e162'[Date])))
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(3500, __DS0Core, [MinDate], [Total_Sales], 350, , ALPHABETICAL, ASC, 105000, 60)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_9ebde1cd-ecfd-4ede-942a-fd7823e3e162'[Year]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Walmart'[Month],
			"Running_Total_Sales_Month", 'Walmart'[Running_Total_Sales_Month]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [Running_Total_Sales_Month], 0, 'Walmart'[Month], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[Running_Total_Sales_Month] DESC, 'Walmart'[Month]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Walmart'[Store], "Total_Sales_Per_Store", 'Walmart'[Total_Sales_Per_Store])

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		SAMPLE(3502, __DS0Core, 'Walmart'[Store], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'Walmart'[Store]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_9ebde1cd-ecfd-4ede-942a-fd7823e3e162'[Year],
			"Running_Total_Sales", 'Walmart'[Running_Total_Sales]
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		SAMPLE(3502, __DS0Core, 'LocalDateTable_9ebde1cd-ecfd-4ede-942a-fd7823e3e162'[Year], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_9ebde1cd-ecfd-4ede-942a-fd7823e3e162'[Year]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Walmart'[Holiday_Flag],
			"Avg_Sales_Holiday", 'Walmart'[Avg_Sales_Holiday],
			"Avg_Sales_Non_Holiday", 'Walmart'[Avg_Sales_Non_Holiday]
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, [Avg_Sales_Holiday], 0, 'Walmart'[Holiday_Flag], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[Avg_Sales_Holiday] DESC, 'Walmart'[Holiday_Flag]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Walmart'[Store], "SumUnemployment", CALCULATE(SUM('Walmart'[Unemployment])))

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		SAMPLE(3502, __DS0Core, 'Walmart'[Store], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'Walmart'[Store]
